high_descs: Go forward and stand at the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the green cupl from the counter.
Turn to the right and face the sink.
Put the bowl in the sink, turn on the water and then off and pick the cup up from the sink.
Turn to the left to face the microwave.
Put the cup in the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cup in the microwave.

high_descs: Face right then back again to walk straight to the counter next to the stove.
Take the green cup off of the counter.
Turn to your right and walk to the sink with the cup.
Put the cup in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water back off and take out the cup.
Turn to your left facing the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the cup next to the apple on the plate and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Clean a cup to place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk straight into the kitchen to the counter immediately to the left of the stove top.
Pick up the green glass that is to the left of the stove top near the edge of the counter.
Holding the green glass, turn right ninety degrees and walk straight to the sink.
Put the green glass upright into the sink. Close the drain and fill the sink with water, rinsing the glass.  Then drain the sink and take the green glass out of the sink.
Turn to the left ninety degrees to face the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the green glass inside the microwave to the right of the apple, and close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Put the rinsed green glass into the microwave.

high_descs: walk to the stove
grab the green cup by the stove
turn right, walk to the sink
put the cup in the sink, wash the cup with water, take the cup
turn left to microwave
open the microwave, put the cup in the microwave, close the microwave
anns.task_desc: grab the green cup by the stove, wash the cup, put it in the microwave
